
<#import "taglib/spring.ftl" as spring />
<#include "taglib/taglib.ftl">
<#include "mobile/template/front/general/macro/macro_help.ftl">
<html>
<head>

<title>帮助-置顶公众号【卓玛拉山】-群侠户外</title>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container " id="body_content">
<@M_homeNavigate/>
<h3 class="text-center">将公众号置顶</h3>
<p class="text-center">微信[wechat]通用</p>
<p>
1.长按二维码，点识别
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/1.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="1.长按二维码，点识别"/>
</p>
<p class="bg-warning">
2.点击‘关注公众号’卓玛拉山
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/2.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="2.点击‘关注公众号’卓玛拉山"/>
</p>
<p>
3.点击‘右上角’图标
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/3.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="3.点击‘右上角’图标"/>
</p>
<p class="bg-warning">
4.继续点击‘右上角 ...’图标
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/4.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="4.继续点击‘右上角 ...’图标"/>
</p>
<p class="bg-warning">
5.点击‘置顶公众号’
<img src="/assets/common/help/topInWechat/5o_topInWechat.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="5.点击‘置顶公众号’"/>
</p>
<p class="bg-warning">
6.查看已置顶：卓玛拉山
<img src="/assets/common/help/topInWechat/6o_topInWechat.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="6.查看已置顶：卓玛拉山"/>
</p>
<@M_homeNavigate/>
</div>
</body>
</html>